Individual




Frederick H. Eppinger



Mr. Frederick H. Eppinger is on the Board of Directors at Stewart Information Services Corp. and Centene Corp. Mr. Eppinger was previously employed as President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by The Hanover Insurance Group, Inc., EVP-Property, Casualty Field & Service Operations by The Hartford Financial Services Group, Inc., Senior Vice President-Strategic Marketing by ChannelPoint, Inc., Partner by McKinsey & Co., Inc., and Accountant by Coopers & Lybrand LLP. He received his undergraduate degree from the College of the Holy Cross (Massachusetts) and an MBA from Dartmouth College.



